results.name: Triangle read by rows: T(n,k) = number of parts in the k-th region of n.
example: Row n has length A000041(n). Row sums give A006128, n >= 1. Right border gives A000041, n >= 1. Records in every row give A000041, n >= 1. Rows converge to A194446.
